  "instructions": [
    "Bring the seafood stock to a boil in a large pot over high heat",
    "Add the egg noodles to the pot and cook according to package instructions",
    "In a large skillet, heat the olive oil over medium-high heat",
    "Add the shrimp, mussels, and scallops to the skillet and cook until the seafood is opaque and cooked through",
    "Stir in the chopped parsley and dill, and cook for an additional minute",
    "Drain the cooked noodles and add them to the skillet with the seafood",
    "Pour the lemon juice over the noodles and seafood, and toss to combine",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste",
    "Serve the noodles and seafood hot, garnished with additional parsley and dill if desired"
  ],
